I reviewed your product Martvili and Okatse Canyons Full Day Tour (130729P18). Since this product offers boat ride for the travelers, TripAdvisor encourages you to have Product Liability Insurance for any water or air tours, like helicopter flights, hot air balloon rides, sky diving, cruises, sailing tours, scuba diving, etc. as it is considered to be "High Risk activities".&nbsp;<br clear="none" class="">
<br clear="none" class="">
Any aspect of a product includes an air or water component (ex. a historical tour where you take a ferry), you need to provide Product Liability Insurance documentation, regardless if you operate the air or water component of the activity<br clear="none" class="">
<br clear="none" class="">
